我们要追溯温斯顿去世前的事情
trace back Winston's last moments.

80
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:11,560
你能想起什么吗?
Can you think of anything?

81
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,080
他要去见一个客户
He was meeting with a client

82
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,880
但我们不确定他有没有见到
but we're just not sure whether he met with him or not.

83
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:19,480
嗯 他确实说要去见一个人
Well, he did say he was meeting someone.

84
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:24,040
所以不能留在这 我当时很生气
That's why he couldn't stay. I got really upset.

85
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,840
就这时候他给了我这块表
That's when he gave me the watch.

86
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,800
要是出了什么意外 把这个给我妻子
If something goes wrong, give this to my wife.

87
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,280
我知道这要求有点过分
I know that's a lot to ask.

88
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:39,160
确实很过分
That is a lot to ask.

89
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,160
他拿着一个棕色的文件袋和一些照片
So a brown folder and some photographs.

90
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:49,680
你知道他走的时候往哪里走了吗?
Did you see which way he went when he left?

91
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,920
他是... 走着还是坐人力车?
Did he... did he walk or take a rickshaw?

92
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:56,960
我不知道这有没有帮助
Well, I don't know if it helps,

93
00:07:57,080 --> 00:08:01,200
但他说过要是事情顺利的话
but he did say if things went well,

94
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:06,000
他去德霖路那家店买我最喜欢的蛋糕
he would buy me my favourite cakes from the shop at Teck Lim Road.

95
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:25,440
就是这家店 温斯顿经常来的
Well, that's the shop, alright. Winston came here all the time.

96
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:28,280
但她不记得那晚他来了没有
But she can't remember whether he was here that night, though.

97
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,760
已经过去太久了
It's been so long.

98
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:36,880
- 你还好吗?  - 嗯 我还好
- You alright? - Yeah. I'm alright.

99
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:43,320
如果他在角落里或者在店外面见的客户
Well, if he met the client at a corner or outside a shop,

100
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,880
那就无踪可寻了
there'd be no trace.

101
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:49,080
温斯顿有最喜欢的咖啡店或者是餐厅吗?
Did Winston have a favourite kopi shop or restaurant?

102
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,800
我不确定
I'm not sure.

103
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:55,360
如果他在餐厅或者咖啡店里见的面
If he met inside a restaurant or kopitiam,

104
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,080
没人会记得
no one would remember.

105
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,840
- 德霖路 - 什么?
- Teck Lim Road. - What?

