00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:46,600
齐基特的办公室 齐基特和温斯顿认识
Chee Kit's office. Chee Kit and Winston knew each other.

108
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:49,640
- 有可能齐基特就是这个客户 - 有可能
- Perhaps Chee Kit is the client. - It's gotta be.

109
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,193
为什么我要告诉你?  
Why should I tell you anything?  

110
00:09:56,194 --> 00:09:57,440
你不会有任何损失
You've got nothing to lose.

111
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,911
你弟弟还是想你死  
Your brother still wants you dead. 

112
00:09:59,912 --> 00:10:01,760
不用考虑我弟弟了
My brother does not concern you.

113
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:06,187
告诉我 你为谁工作?  
But tell me,who do you work for?  

114
00:10:06,188 --> 00:10:07,640
帕特丽夏・郑
Patricia Cheng.

115
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:10,400
你雇佣了她的丈夫 温斯顿
You hired her husband, Winston.

116
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,720
他被杀的那晚你在德霖路的工会办公室
Did you meet with him the night he was killed

117
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,640
和他见过面吗?
at the Trade Union office on Teck Lim Road?

118
