没有 他一直没出现
No. He never turned up.

119
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:22,640
第二天 我就听说他在一场抢劫中被杀了
And the next day, I heard he was killed in a robbery.

120
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:26,720
- 你相信吗? - 这也是有可能的
- Do you believe that? - It wasn't impossible.

121
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,840
你在调查谁?
Who were you investigating?

122
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:44,320
我觉得我弟弟和一些危险人物有关系
I believe my brother was involved with some dangerous people.

123
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,278
我只是想知道  
I just wanted to know.  

124
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:49,200
所以你让温斯顿跟踪詹姆士?
So you had Winston follow James?

125
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:52,960
- 你也不会出现在客户名单上? - 对
- You were never listed as a client? - No.

126
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:56,380
温斯顿 他有自己的方法 
Winston, he had a system. 

127
00:10:56,381 --> 00:10:59,640
把我的案子写成不忠的案例
He wrote it up as an infidelity case.

128
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:04,760
当然 他自己真的有外遇 情况很复杂
Of course, he was actually having an affair, which complicated things,

129
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:09,840
但我对他的外遇不感兴趣
but I wasn't interested in his affairs with women.

130
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:13,960
我想知道他跟其他人的会面
I wanted to know about his other meetings.

131
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:17,160
所以当晚他是去送照片的?
So he was delivering photographs that night?

132
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,880
是的
Yes.

133
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:24,520
但不知为什么我弟弟发现我在调查他
But somehow my brother found out that I was investigating him.

134
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:29,080
然后他雇人阻止了温斯顿
And he paid for someone to intercept Winston.

135
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,720
李库方 你认识他吗?
Lee Kum Fong, do you know him?

136
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,840
不认识
No.

137
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,203
那你从没看过任何照片? 
So you never saw any photographs? 

138
00:11:36,204 --> 00:11:38,040
你也不知道里面有谁?
You don't know who was in them?

139
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,440
不知道
No.

140
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:44,760
唯一知道真相的人就是我弟弟
The only one who can tell you is my brother,

141
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:48,960
但他为了保密已经杀过人了
but he has already killed once to keep it secret.

